data.description: A module that parses MPEG frames from FHs
data.PS: The following links are only valid for module list maintainers:
data.rationale:
The module is a pure perl, simple implementation of MPEG stream
    parsing. It can be used to dissect, possibly dirty streams, transfer
    mp3 data via a network more efficiently, and so forth.

    The module deals with frames as objects, which have various methods
    which return attributes, aswell as the parsed data.
